---
const LAWYER = 'Nilufer';
---
<section id="about" class="bg-neutral-950 py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="container mx-auto grid gap-12 px-4 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">About {LAWYER}</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 leading-relaxed">I am a UK‑qualified Solicitor and TR‑qualified Advocate with a Master’s degree in Business. I combine deep legal expertise with commercial acumen to deliver strategic advice and practical solutions on complex legal and compliance matters. Over 20 years in practice, I have managed and advised on high‑profile projects and transactions across multiple regions and industries, including energy, infrastructure, and finance.</p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lotus-600"></span><span>Cross‑border structuring, negotiations, and regulatory alignment</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lotus-600"></span><span>High‑value commercial contracts with clear risk allocation</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lotus-600"></span><span>M&amp;A due diligence and end‑to‑end transaction support</span></li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lotus-600"></span><span>Energy sector expertise; experience with London‑listed operators</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lotus-600"></span><span>Cross‑cultural bridge: European & Eastern business environments</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lotus-600"></span><span>Leadership & teaching: oil & gas law at the Turkish Bar Association</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Credentials / Accreditations -->
      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Credentials</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-white/80">
          <li class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">UK Solicitor</li>
          <li class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">TR Advocate</li>
          <li class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">MSc in Business</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Highlights -->
      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Highlights</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-medium text-white/60">Industries</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-white/80">
              <li>Energy (Oil & Gas)</li>
              <li>Infrastructure</li>
              <li>Finance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-medium text-white/60">Regions Served</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-white/80">
              <li>UK & Europe</li>
              <li>Middle East</li>
              <li>Cross‑border engagements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Values / Approach -->
      <div class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Approach</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
          <li>Clarity first: align legal strategy with business outcomes</li>
          <li>Bridge cultures: adapt frameworks across jurisdictions</li>
          <li>Risk‑forward: identify issues early; negotiate durable positions</li>
          <li>Collaborative: transparent, research‑led problem solving</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-white/60">Outside work: paragliding, windsurfing, skiing, and horseback riding—disciplines that, like complex transactions, reward preparation, judgment, and calm decision‑making.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -inset-6 -z-10 rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-tr from-lotus-600/20 via-purple-600/10 to-indigo-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur">
        <!-- Portrait / Accreditations area (placeholder) -->
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="/Nilufer-Ozder-Genel-Energy-thumbnail.jpg" alt="Portrait of {LAWYER}" class="h-14 w-14 rounded-full object-cover" width="56" height="56" loading="lazy" />
          <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px] text-white/70">
            <li class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-1">UK Solicitor</li>
            <li class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-1">TR Advocate</li>
            <li class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-1">MSc Business</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/80">
          <p>“I admire very much the unique blend of legal, commercial, and cultural skills she displays when dealing with the knotty issues that can arise in the oil sector in developing jurisdictions, making her an asset to the business and a pleasure to work with.”</p>
          <footer class="mt-4 text-xs font-medium text-white/60">— Paula Hodges KC, Partner & Head of Global Arbitration, Herbert Smith Freehills LLP</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
